{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_cgbird_set_1", "eventName": "藍色羽毛與歌", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "藍色羽毛與歌", "storyInfo": "萊塔尼亞的邊遠村莊裡，又一個病重的孩子因夜鶯和臨光的幫助而重拾希望。可是身為醫者的夜鶯自己，身體已經瀕臨極限。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "4:37 P. M. 天氣/晴"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞東北部某村莊"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，咳咳......", "name": "虛弱的孩子"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼辦啊，盧卡他看起來越來越難受了。", "name": "焦急的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_069"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽，我好疼啊......好疼......我的腿，我腿上像是有火在燒。", "name": "虛弱的孩子"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，盧卡，你忍一下，不能叫太大聲。隔壁湯瑪斯家會聽見的。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是最堅強的男子漢。要是忍不了的話，就咬住這枕頭吧。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棉花都要被咬爛啦！他出了這麼多汗，而且還在發燒。我......我們還是帶他去找馬科斯醫生吧？", "name": "焦急的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_069"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。這行不通的。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看看，你看看他的腿......這一小塊黑黑的東西。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是礦石......", "name": "焦急的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_069"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，不要說出來，現在別說出來。別讓盧卡聽見。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上回雅尼克家的本，他的手上也長出了這個，然後他就被帶走了。你知道的，他們再也沒讓他回來。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......盧卡......我的盧卡，絕不能讓他們把他帶走。", "name": "焦急的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_069"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只能這樣子。我們只能這樣......熬過去。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽......媽媽......", "name": "虛弱的孩子"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咬這個吧，咬爸爸的手。盧卡，再忍一忍......我的小男子漢，你會好起來的。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會有奇跡......我相信會有奇跡發生。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只能相信。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問有人嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.25}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敲門聲！竟然有人在這時候找上門，他們是來帶走盧卡的嗎？", "name": "焦急的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_069"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "avg_npc_068", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別害怕，我去窗戶那裡看一眼。你抱著盧卡，待在房間裡別出來。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_069", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltstrongpoint", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.7}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，先生。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫蘭塔？看打扮還是個騎士？我們這種小村子裡可不多見。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，你不用擔心，我們只是幾個流浪的醫者，剛好路過這裡，想問你借一杯水喝。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......好。只是一杯水，你要是敢喝，我當然也不會拒絕。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連這個杯子一起拿去吧。喝完趕緊走。", "name": "無奈的父親"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，麗茲？我想這水沒有問題。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感覺到了......無聲的痛苦......就在這裡。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。雖然微弱，但很清晰。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人在呼救。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你們這麼說——", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先生，請問你家有礦石病患者嗎？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦石病！你、你怎麼敢！", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他很疼吧？可還沒有絕望。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以......治療他。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......這個角......這個角的形狀！你、還有你，你們是魔族人！", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，請你冷靜一下。就像我剛才介紹的，我們是醫生。如果你家裡真有礦石病患者，我們可以幫助他緩解病情。這並不需要任何回報。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經說了——我們這裡沒有病人，更不需要什麼治療！", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走吧，滿嘴謊言的庫蘭塔！還有你們，魔族人，你們離我家遠一些！", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#3"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_outcounty"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來那位先生打定了主意，不願意讓我們治療他的家人。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "類似的事情並不少見。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通常情況下，醫者與病人之間必須建立信賴關係。而他無法信任我們。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看起來很緊張。或許因為我們的身份，讓他產生了戒備心理。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這回連一貫很受歡迎的臨光都敗下陣來，更不必說我與麗茲。薩卡茲的名聲在哪裡都不夠好。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我們可以嘗試說服這位先生，就像以前很多次那樣。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前提是我們沒有遇上憲兵隊。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。說服一隊憲兵，要比說服一位病人的親屬困難得多。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們目前需要儘量避免那種“說服”。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這段時間麗茲的身體一直不太好......我同意，我們不該冒險。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是可惜那位病人，拖下去的話，情況會越來越糟。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很難受。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茲，你哪裡不舒服嗎？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個孩子，他很難受......他被關在那個小小的房間裡，忍受著病痛的煎熬。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茲說的對，那個孩子確實被關著。就連痛呼都是壓抑著的。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說他們在虐待感染者？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是這樣。那位父親......他在提到礦石病的時候，臉上並沒有流露仇恨。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在其他地方，仇恨遍地都是。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，莫非是為了保護病人？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說萊塔尼亞人會把感染者從家裡帶走，讓他們集中起來生活。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果得病的真是剛才那位先生的孩子，他是不希望孩子被憲兵帶走，才想拼命捂住這個消息吧？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這份關心，正在漸漸帶走他孩子的生命。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "困在名為愛的牢籠裡，錯過生存的希望，全身的活力漸漸枯竭......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茲！", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不要再想這些了。悲傷的情緒會對你的身體造成負累。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天趕了很多路，你的疲憊肉眼可見。你需要休息。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靠著我會不會好一些？帳篷快搭好了。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生個火，吃些東西。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天快黑了。萊塔尼亞的憲兵隊速度很快。他們或許明天就會來到這裡，為了避免麻煩，我們最好在他們到來之前離開。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，出現在他們面前不是很好的選擇。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茲，我扶你在這躺下。這裡離火堆更近，暖和些。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休息吧，我會守著你們。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是憲兵隊。他們果然來了。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈你醒了？明明才睡下沒多久。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠久了。我們馬上離開這裡。麗茲，你能走嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，可以的。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的臉色看起來很蒼白。昨晚沒有休息好嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我還好，只是有些頭暈。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憲兵隊的人衝著昨天那位先生家裡去了。閃靈，我們真的應該就這樣離開嗎？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......灌木叢後面的位置還算隱蔽。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躲在這裡的話，他們看不到我們。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨光，扶好麗茲。萬一情況不對，隨機應變。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltstrongpoint", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊斯先生！請您把門打開。", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊斯先生！", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憲兵先生，您瞧！我就說老萊斯家裡有問題！", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前些日子他家小兒子——那個叫盧卡的男孩，從附近田地玩耍回來，突然就病倒了。", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後這幾天，他家就關緊了大門，任誰叫都不出來。", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我只是為了照顧盧卡......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這話我沒法相信！是什麼病會讓一個結實的孩子一病不起？", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，要是盧卡真的只是簡簡單單的生病，你們為何不帶他去找馬科斯醫生？", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來是不大對勁。", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是吧，憲兵先生！我這是為了大家的安全考慮！", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這裡......這美好而寧靜的村子，可經不起礦石病的肆虐啊！", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。所有感染者都必須集中到附近的隔離區去。", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對嘛！老萊斯，你聽聽。只是去隔離區而已，在那裡小盧卡會得到更好的照顧，不比藏在家裡好？", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是什麼呢，萊斯先生？您今天必須把這門打開。", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，爸爸，你快點開門吧。", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都餓壞了，我想吃麵包。一片不夠，我現在可以一口氣吃下五六片呢。", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦——咦？！", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是湯瑪斯叔叔，真抱歉撞到了您。我急著回家吃早飯，不然我媽媽一定會罵我的。", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧卡啊，你總算回來了。一大早就跑出門，玩了這麼久才回來。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真不好意思啊憲兵先生，這就是我兒子盧卡。不是我不願意開門，是他剛才確實不在家。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這健壯活潑的孩子就是盧卡？他真的在生病嗎？", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，一點小風寒罷了。這個年紀的小男孩，誰不會因為貪玩而生點小病呢？", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看也是。我見過的感染者多了去了，沒有哪個像這樣活蹦亂跳的。馬科斯醫生，您說呢？", "name": "萊塔尼亞憲兵"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦......哦？您是說檢查嗎？我來看一眼。", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧瞧這結實的小胳膊，全是汗，摸起來平平整整。", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有腿......", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，真是有力的小腿。挺多泥巴的，這孩子剛剛玩得真瘋。", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "緊張的鄰居"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給馬科斯醫生添麻煩了。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦......好啦！憲兵先生，這忙了一個大清早，我的肚子也餓得咕咕叫，老眼昏花的，再也看不出啥了。", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們放這小夥子回家吃麵包吧？", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不必擔心，要是後面小盧卡又生病了，我會好好檢查。有問題的話一定通知您。", "name": "年邁的醫生"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，好險......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧卡，我的小男子漢，快讓爸爸好好瞧瞧！", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的......真的好了？有力氣跑跳，也吃得下飯......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些礦石......倒是還在，小了許多，邊緣也沒那麼紅腫了，瞧起來好了不少，難怪馬科斯醫生第一眼沒發現。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這就是奇跡嗎？", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，不是奇跡，是小羽獸把我治好啦！", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......小羽獸？", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是好漂亮、好漂亮的羽獸啊！它的羽毛比最藍的湖水還要藍！我從來沒有見過這麼好看的小羽獸！", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天晚上，它從窗戶裡飛了進來，停在我的床頭。", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一團潔白的光包裹著這隻小小的羽獸。那個光，好明亮，又好溫暖......", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們一起靠向我，我一下子就感覺不到痛了。", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻羽獸？還是會發光的羽獸？", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！千真萬確呀！", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可憐的孩子，一定是你病糊塗了，生出了幻覺。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是幻覺，還有歌呢，我真的聽到了，那隻藍色的小羽獸在對我唱歌！", "name": "活潑的孩子"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_068"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好，沒事了，沒事了......", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，神奇的藍色羽獸，無論你是真的假的——當然是假的——無論如何，謝謝你給了我的盧卡一個美夢。", "name": "無奈的父親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_068"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們該走了。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你沒有生氣吧？", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼而生氣呢？為了那隻趁著夜色飛去病人身邊的小鳥嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對，那隻鳥還會發光。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#3"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，咳咳咳。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#3"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉閃靈。昨天晚上，我看麗茲無法安眠......", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#7"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈，是我請求臨光幫助我去治療那孩子的。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則我......我睡不著。我一直醒著，腦子裡都是那孩子痛苦的呻吟。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是我的腿......要不是我的腿沒力氣，我會自己去。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不要責怪臨光。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不需要道歉。我們本就是醫者，你們只不過做了該做的事。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到今天憲兵隊真的來人了......不知道那孩子和他的家人之後會怎樣。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許會從此安生度日，又或許用不了多久，他們就必須搬家。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫者只能撫平一時的傷痛，沒有辦法真的將壞的變成好的。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道的，閃靈，可是我想不了那麼多。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那個孩子，他很疼很疼。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看著他，就好像我也很疼很疼。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我只知道我能讓他不那麼疼。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想幫助他......我可以幫他減輕病痛......我想幫他離開那房間，讓他重新跑起來、跳起來。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麗茲，我只有一個問題。你看著我。你告訴我，你是覺得自己必須這麼做嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼是......必須？", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像過去那樣。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去那樣......我不想像過去那樣。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候是他們來找我。我被關著......哪裡都去不了。我不得不去治療他們。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在呢？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在......現在是我走很多地方。我去找他們。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我找到那些生病的、受傷的人。我感受他們的痛苦。我希望他們不要繼續痛下去。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我伸出雙手......擁抱他們的傷痛。我讓我的小鳥，去他們耳畔唱歌。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒想到，那孩子能看見我的小鳥。他在睡夢中笑得很高興。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那個時候，我的眼前......那些亂亂的、始終扎著我的碎片不見了。小鳥的舞蹈也變得很輕盈。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是不是就是高興？閃靈，這麼說的話，我似乎也很高興。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。這是我要的答案。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，麗茲，這就是高興。你懂得什麼是高興了。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#2"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是這樣嗎？原來這就是高興？那我現在也......唔......嗯......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很難受。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，閃靈......我好像很難受。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......麗茲為什麼會變成這樣？她甚至沒有站起來的力氣了。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為她的選擇。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......因為她在昨天晚上治療了那個孩子？", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。她的身體狀況本來就很糟糕，使用簡單的治療法術也會對她造成負擔，何況是處理急性礦石病。現在她越來越......瀕臨極限。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道這樣的話......", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道這樣的話，你會阻止她嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我想那樣做。我想治療那個孩子。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽，這就是麗茲的願望。哪怕她因此而傷痕累累。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的......閃靈，我想我沒有辦法阻止她。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這就是選擇——你們的選擇。你和麗茲一樣，為了拯救看得見或者看不見的苦痛，你們總是會選擇犧牲自己的一切。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本該......尊重你們的選擇。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閃靈......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我希望......我希望，麗茲還能有更多的選擇。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你，瑪嘉烈。我希望你也能有更多的選擇。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更多的選擇，那是什麼意思呢？", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是一直想看看外面的世界嗎，麗茲？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，這是我最大的心願。我跟著你，閃靈，我們和臨光一起，已經走了許多地方。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些地方......很美。有時候，仇恨和傷痛遮蓋了天空和大地，而我依然能看到疤痕下面流淌著的美麗。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想......我還想看到更多。不僅僅是我的小鳥兒唱給我聽的那些。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1", "name2": "char_147_shining_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是時候去看看更廣闊的世界了。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛好像做了一個決定，閃靈。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨光，你還記得上次那個病人提到的醫藥公司嗎？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說......羅德島。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#2", "name2": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，羅德島。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#2"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#2"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在一起行走的這些年，一共治療了多少病人？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不記得了。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不記得也沒關係。麗茲，想不想一起去治癒更多人？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想......我想去。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。那你呢，臨光？", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島嗎......我沒有異議。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信你，也願意相信你的決定。如果麗茲想去，那麼我們就帶她去。", "name": "臨光"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#5"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一起......", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#2"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們一起。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#2"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_147_shining_1#1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然已經決定，那麼，就出發吧。", "name": "閃靈"}, "figure_art": "char_147_shining_1#1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_179_cgbird_1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出發。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......去羅德島。", "name": "夜鶯"}, "figure_art": "char_179_cgbird_1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}